      "description": "CFD-predicted relative hemolysis index (RH) compared against in-vitro measurements across 5 flow-rate and rotational-speed combinations. All 5 predictions satisfy RH < 1 acceptance criterion. Mean absolute error 0.043 RH units; maximum deviation 0.091 RH units. Turbulence model: SST k-omega with curvature correction. Blood rheology: Carreau–Yasuda non-Newtonian model with hematocrit 40%.",
