      "description": "Simulated pump pressure head compared against manufacturer bench-test data at 3 rotational speeds (2400, 3000, 3600 RPM) across the full operating flow range. R² = 0.987; maximum relative error 3.2% at lowest flow rate. Validates momentum transport fidelity as a prerequisite to hemolysis field accuracy.",
      "hasUncertaintyQuantification": {
        "id": "https://uofa.net/morrison/uq/vr-02-uq",
        "type": "UncertaintyQuantification",
