      "name": "Wall Shear Stress Distribution — PIV Comparison",
      "description": "Time-averaged wall shear stress fields compared against particle image velocimetry (PIV) measurements in the volute and impeller passages. Qualitative agreement confirmed in high-shear regions near blade leading edges; quantitative comparison limited to regions accessible by PIV optics. Normalised RMS difference 8.4% over accessible domain.",
      "hasUncertaintyQuantification": {
