      "rationale": "In-vitro hemolysis tests conducted per ASTM F1841 protocol using bovine blood at hematocrit 40% ± 2%. Flow rates measured with Coriolis meter (±0.5%); rotational speed via optical tachometer (±10 RPM). Temperature maintained 37°C ± 0.5°C. All deviations from nominal conditions recorded and propagated as input uncertainty in UQ analysis."
