      "rationale": "Turbulence model sensitivity study (VR-05) characterises model-form uncertainty as ±3.4% RH. Hemolysis power-law model coefficients sourced from Giersiepen et al. with coefficient uncertainty propagated via Monte Carlo. Dominant model-form source identified as turbulence closure; magnitude acceptable relative to RH < 1 decision threshold."
